Package: tica
Type: Package
Title: Modelling land transitions impacts in the Cerrado and Amazon
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hugo Tameirão Seixas
Maintainer: Hugo Tameirão Seixas <seixas.hugo@protonmail.com>
Description: This is a package designed to run a model that will estimate land transitions and their impact in the Cerrado and Amazon
    The functions are responsible for downloading external data, organizing them in a common grid, and then running a series of statistical models.
